1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,359
[SPEAKER_01] Dobrodošli u Launched.

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam Charlie Chapman i danas sam uzbuđen što vam predstavljam nezavisnog programera aplikacija iza iznimno popularnog WidgetSmita, Davida Smitha.

3
00:00:23,359 --> 00:00:25,120
[SPEAKER_00] David, hvala ti što si došao.

4
00:00:25,440 --> 00:00:27,199
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala ti što si me primio.

5
