58
00:05:05,199 --> 00:05:06,160
[SPEAKER_00] I tako sam to učinio.

59
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:11,680
[SPEAKER_00] I tako sam, na neki način, napustio posao i počeo raditi web konzultancije.

60
00:05:11,759 --> 00:05:14,000
